<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3734] HBaseAdmin creates new configurations in getCatalogTracker</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3734</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HBaseAdmin.getCatalogTracker creates new Configuration every time it&apos;s called, instead HBA should reuse the same one and do the copy inside the constructor.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12503365">HBASE-3734</key>
            <summary>HBaseAdmin creates new configurations in getCatalogTracker</summary>
